OL,6,FA 54-year-old woman died after a
OL,7,Fgastric sleeve operation in Turkey, an
OL,8,Finquest heard.
OL,10,FJanet Lynne Savage, from Gwynedd, had
OL,11,Fcontacted a travel company after
OL,12,Fdeciding she wanted to lose three
OL,13,Fstone.
OL,15,FBut the driving examiner, from
OL,16,FPenrhosgarnedd near Bangor, was taken
OL,17,Fto an intensive care unit and could
OL,18,Fnot be saved after problems developed
OL,19,Fduring the procedure which took place
OL,20,Fat a private hospital.
