OL,6,FShe was found to have died from acute
OL,7,Fbleeding loss due to injury to her
OL,8,Fabdominal aorta, which had an
OL,9,Fattempted repair, due to gastric
OL,10,Fsleeve surgery, said a senior coroner
OL,11,Fat the inquest into her death, held in
OL,12,FCaernarfon.
OL,14,FMrs Savage had contacted a firm called
OL,15,FReginis Health Travel, based in
OL,16,FStratford-upon-Avon in Warwickshire,
OL,17,Fwhich arranges flights, hotels,
OL,18,Fsurgical and non-surgical procedures
OL,19,Fat the private Ozel Rich Hospital in
OL,20,FKiziltoprak in southern Turkey.
