OL,6,FA statement by Alison Ergun, Reginis'
OL,7,Fclient service administrator, was read
OL,8,Fout at the inquest by senior coroner
OL,9,Ffor north-west Wales, Kate Robertson.
OL,11,FIn the statement, Ms Ergun said Mrs
OL,12,FSavage told her in an exchange of
OL,13,FFacebook messages in July last year
OL,14,Fthat she was taking Ozempic (a
OL,15,Fmedicine designed to treat people with
OL,16,Ftype 2 diabetes) and wanted to lose
OL,17,Fthree stone.
