OL,6,FMrs Savage was "worried" about the
OL,7,Fsurgeon and asked for information
OL,8,Fabout him, said Ms Ergun. The
OL,9,Foperation was arranged for the
OL,10,Fhospital in Anatalya for August 5 last
OL,11,Fyear after the women spoke over
OL,12,FWhatsApp.
OL,14,FMs Ergun said she was then informed by
OL,15,Fher operations manager that there had
OL,16,Fbeen "complications", and that Mrs
OL,17,FSavage had been taken to intensive
OL,18,Fcare after she had stopped breathing.
OL,19,FShe died the next day, at 7.45am on
OL,20,FAugust 6.
