OL,6,FMrs Savage's family arrived in Antalya
OL,7,Flater that day, said Ms Ergun, who
OL,8,Fwent with them to the hospital. Via a
OL,9,Ftranslator Mrs Savage's relatives were
OL,10,Ftold she'd had a heart attack and
OL,11,Fthere had been "serious internal
OL,12,Fbleeding".
