OL,6,FMs Ergun said the family "thanked" her
OL,7,Ffor her efforts and she escorted them
OL,8,Fback to the airport afterwards. The
OL,9,Finquest also heard from a hospital
OL,10,Fdoctor who told how Mrs Savage had had
OL,11,Fa "major artery trauma" which was
OL,12,Frepaired and blood was replaced. She
OL,13,Fthen developed an arrest during the
OL,14,Fsurgery, said the doctor.
OL,16,F"Despite all the interventions the
OL,17,Fpatient was confirmed as having passed
OL,18,Faway," said Dr Ramazan Azar in a
OL,19,Fstatement. The coroner ordered a post-
OL,20,Fmortem examination after Mrs Savage's
OL,21,Fbody was returned to the UK.
