OL,7,Fcarried out but Mrs Savage died on
OL,8,FAugust 6. The cause of death was given
OL,9,Fas acute blood loss due to injury to
OL,10,Fthe abdominal aorta with repair due to
OL,11,Fgastric sleeve surgery.
